# Reliz tag (GitHub)

`package.json` dagi `version` oshirilib `main` ga commit + `git push origin main` qilingandan **keyin**, har doim:

1. Versiyani o‘qing (masalan `1.1.3`).
2. Annotated tag yarating: `git tag -a v<VERSIYA> -m "E-Savdo v<VERSIYA>"` (masalan `v1.1.3`).
3. Tag ni yuboring: `git push origin v<VERSIYA>`.

Agar tag allaqachon mavjud bo‘lsa, qayta yaratmang; faqat kerak bo‘lsa `git push origin v<VERSIYA>` tekshiring.

Bu tag `.github/workflows/release-win.yml` dagi `v*` trigger orqali Windows reliz buildini ishga tushiradi.
